quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,62,"Anndu gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen ko …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on, si …ďe laatike hi…ďe wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftu…óo, …ďe njahatah haa …ďe duŇčinoo e makko, pellet, …ďen …óa…ď…ďiray…ďe ma duŇčayee ko …ďen …óon woni gooŇč…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on, si …ďe …óa…ď…ďirii ma duŇčayee fii yoga e fiyaake ma…ď…ďe, duŇčano on mo yi…ó…óaa [duŇčanaade] e ma…ď…ďe, imsinano…óaa …ďe ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko cuhroowo jurmetee…óo."
  24,63,"Wota on mba…ó noddugol Nulaa…óo on hakkunde moo…óon wano noddugol yoga e moo…óon yoga. GooŇč…óii Alla no Anndi …ďeen sortotoo…ďe e moo…óon e moltagol, …ďen won…ďe lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo …ďe rento fii wata fitina hi…ďu …ďe maa…óum Lempte mu'usu…óe he…ďa …ďe."
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gooŇč…óii homo Anndi ko ngon…óon e hoore mu'um kon, √Ďande …ďe nduttetee fa'ade ka makko p yeetoo …ďe ko …ďe ngollunoo kon. Alla ko O ganndu…óo kala hu'unde."
  25,1,"Mawnii On Jippin…óo Seerndoore nden e dow jiyaa…óo makko on fii yo wonan winndire nden jeertinoowo."
  25,2,"Oon mo woodanii …óum Laamu kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, o jogitaaki …ďi…ó…óo laatanaaki mo kadi kafidaa…óo ka Laamu. O tagii kala hu'unde O e…ď…ďindiinde e e…ď…ďugol."